title: BARD - Newsom 2024 & YouTube Strikes
itunes:title: BARD - Newsom 2024 & YouTube Strikes
description:
Adam and Mark reunite in studio and discuss both the chances that Gavin Newsom will end up the Democratic Presidential nominee in 2024 as well as his track record on homelessness. As the show wraps up they discuss how Mark recently got a strike on Adam's YouTube channel.

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
